cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY 

This paper deals with sentiment analysis of Arabic language, specifically Jordanian colloquial reviews. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms such as Support Vector Machines (SVM), which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves the use of lexicons and estimation methods, which falls under the category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The paper also involves the use of sentiment analysis, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper also involves the use of Arabic language, which falls under the category of cs.CY (Computing and Society).
